comment.rvariables: rvariables are all the variables used in the linearization
comment.uvariables: uvariables are compositions of the variables
comment.runits: runits are the SI-units corresponding to the rvariables
comment.uunits: uunits are the SI-units corresponding to the uvariables
comment.errormargins: errormargins are the margins of error for the rvariables
comment.unitpows: just a documentation for the SI-units which occur among the variables
comment.datafilename: name of file containing measurement data
comment.determinedexponents: if an exponent is determined, put it here; if it is not determined, assign it the value 0, if it is determined and 0, why use it?
